title: DeepSeek AI + Helicone
description: Introducing the integration of DeepSeek AI with Helicone's observability platform. This integration enables comprehensive monitoring and analytics for DeepSeek's powerful language models, including their MoE and Code models. Leverage Helicone's advanced observability features to track costs, monitor performance, and optimize your DeepSeek AI implementations while maintaining full visibility into your model interactions and usage patterns.
